{"title":"工作分配问题(job)","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":15,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-4893","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>【问题描述】</p><p>    设有n件工作分配给n个人。将工作i分配给第j个人所需的费用为C<sub>ij</sub>。试设计一个算法，为每一个人都分配一件不同的工作，并使总费用达到最小。<br></p><p>【编程任务】</p><p>    设计一个算法，对于给定的工作费用，计算最佳工作分配方案，使总费用达到最小。<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行有1个正整数n。接下来的n行，每行n个正整数，第i行表示第i个人各项工作费用。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个正整数，计算出的最小总费用</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3<br></p><p>4 2 5</p><p>2 3 6</p><p>3 4 5</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>9</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1&lt;=n&lt;=16</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}